    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take command of your mercenary forces in <strong>Atom Zombie Smasher</strong>. The zombie apocalypse is upon us and it's up to you to evacuate everyone before they fall prey to the undead.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/55040/extras/5ed6e648bbe7428b6e3a63c304f25430.avif?t=1770680696\" width=300 height=178 /></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GROUND CONTROL</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Conduct massive rescue operations with a helping hand from snipers, artillery crews, orbital bombardments, and more. Experience the tactical richness of fully-destructible environments and randomly-generated campaigns.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/55040/extras/4e1dc1b497972f2c66e708f9a08dae91.avif?t=1770680696\" width=300 height=153 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mercs for hire:</strong> Hire and upgrade your ragtag group of snipers, demo teams, orbital bombardment crews, and more.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>No two cities are the same:</strong> Cities are randomly-generated, giving a unique experience with each playthrough.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Destructible environments:</strong> You can absolutely blow up everything.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Play with friends:</strong> Up to three people can cooperatively play together.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mod support:</strong> Mix and modify the game rules however you like.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/55040/extras/82cca77e9f73637b4824a231a076c9d8.avif?t=1770680696\" width=406 height=118 /></span></p>",
